http://vita.had.co.nz/papers/layered-grammar.pdf
  - by Hadley Wickham
  - learn more about the theoretical underpinnings of ggplot2
  
  nb: uses old terminology
  eg: ggplot(data = diamonds, mapping = aes(price)) +
        layer(geom = "bar", stat = "bin",
        mapping = aes(y = ..count..))
      instead of geom_bar it's layer(geom="bar"...)
